Review and Load Data to Power BI Desktop 1

Here is a link to the data and information about it: https://data.cms.gov/Medicare-Inpatient/Inpatient-Prospective-Payment-System-IPPS-Provider/97k6-zzx3

We can view the data in the browser and review it to get a overview.


To download the data, click "Export" and download as CSV for Excel


Now we need to open Power BI Desktop and click "Get Data" and choose the CSV file we just downloaded.


Now we need to click "Edit" to take us to Query Editor where we can transform the data.


If you click on "Load" - you can access Query Editor later via Data tab and click "Edit Queries"
